      "content": "\u003cdiv class\u003d\"introduction img-head\"\u003e\r\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"header\"\u003e\r\n   \u003ch3\u003eFailure Progress Monitoring - Data Studio\u003c/h3\u003e\r\n  \u003c/div\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eOverview\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\n      This app simulates and monitors the progress of a workflow execution while intentionally demonstrating a failure scenario. It is designed to help users understand workflow progress tracking, status updates, and error handling in Data Studio environments.\u003c/section\u003e\r\n\r\n \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eInput\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003eWorkflow execution parameters (e.g., job IDs, step details, runtime parameters).\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003eConfigurations for simulating delays and progress percentage updates.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n       \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eOutput\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003eReal-time progress updates (e.g., 10%, 50%, 80%) during execution.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003eFailure message output for workflow termination simulation.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eBenefits\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003eHelps test and validate progress tracking mechanisms.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003eDemonstrates how failures are reported in a workflow environment.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003eUseful for debugging and improving workflow resilience.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n \r\n      \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\u003c/d